1
00:00:02,502 --> 00:00:03,802
Just a heads-up.

2
00:00:03,803 --> 00:00:04,870
You're still new to this,

3
00:00:04,871 --> 00:00:05,672
but we really need

4
00:00:05,673 --> 00:00:06,940
to land this commercial.

5
00:00:07,974 --> 00:00:10,410
We'll give it our all and see what happens.

6
00:00:11,945 --> 00:00:12,645
Hey,

7
00:00:12,646 --> 00:00:13,679
have you seen the shipping thread

8
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:14,714
about me and Hei Yan?

9
00:00:15,015 --> 00:00:15,882
I'm trying to talk business,

10
00:00:15,883 --> 00:00:17,549
and you're looking at gossip.

11
00:00:17,550 --> 00:00:19,752
Focus, please!

12
00:00:19,753 --> 00:00:20,754
Alright, alright.

13
00:00:22,622 --> 00:00:23,490
Why do I keep

14
00:00:23,491 --> 00:00:24,657
running into you guys?

15
00:00:27,727 --> 00:00:29,162
Are you here for the audition too?

16
00:00:30,930 --> 00:00:32,599
I'll give you a little tip.

17
00:00:32,932 --> 00:00:33,900
Word is the female lead

18
00:00:33,901 --> 00:00:35,235
is already slated for Ko Shasha.

19
00:00:35,835 --> 00:00:37,337
I'm old friends with the client,

20
00:00:38,544 --> 00:00:39,812
so I'm going to go say hi.

21
00:00:43,643 --> 00:00:44,643
Oh, and...

22
00:00:45,912 --> 00:00:46,912
good luck.

23
00:00:52,952 --> 00:00:53,952
What are you doing?

24
00:00:56,589 --> 00:00:57,624
Your tie was crooked.

25
00:00:57,991 --> 00:00:58,991
See you in there.

26
00:01:08,034 --> 00:01:09,235
That Hei Yan guy

27
00:01:09,803 --> 00:01:11,104
is actually pretty decent.

28
00:01:12,272 --> 00:01:13,272
Hey,

29
00:01:13,907 --> 00:01:15,174
don't be so quick to trust people,

30
00:01:15,175 --> 00:01:16,175
okay?

31
00:01:17,177 --> 00:01:18,610
His manager is the jerk,

32
00:01:18,611 --> 00:01:19,878
not him.

33
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:20,946
Why would Lin Bingchen

34
00:01:20,947 --> 00:01:22,649
tell us who the lead is?

35
00:01:23,583 --> 00:01:24,950
It means

36
00:01:24,951 --> 00:01:27,486
we're just here just for show.

37
00:01:27,487 --> 00:01:29,388
Because Hei Yan and Ko Shasha

38
00:01:29,389 --> 00:01:31,224
are with the same agency.

39
00:01:31,577 --> 00:01:32,625
Just for show?

40
00:01:34,494 --> 00:01:35,361
Come on,

41
00:01:35,362 --> 00:01:36,963
at least it's good experience.

42
00:01:38,865 --> 00:01:39,766
Please.

43
00:01:39,767 --> 00:01:41,033
Since I'm working so hard

44
00:01:41,034 --> 00:01:42,034
to promote you,

45
00:01:42,702 --> 00:01:43,735
can you take this seriously

46
00:01:43,736 --> 00:01:44,736
for once?

47
00:01:46,773 --> 00:01:48,241
Stop messing around. Let's go.

48
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,611
Let's go.
